      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "COLUMBUS. O., April S.-The To-\ncal brewery workmen's strike opened\nthis morning with a riot. An attempt\nwas made to keep a carload of nom\nunionists from Pittsburg from going\nto, work. Three strikers were badly\nbeaten by two Pinkerton guards. who\nwere arrested and jailed. charged\nwith assault. Forty police have been\ndetailed as an escort to wagons dis\ntributing beer."
    }
